 人工智能算法研发相关职位 以上数据来自《2021 高校应届生专业就业竞争力报告》互联网公司校招大幅增加入职名额 核心岗位首次开放"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-2939a39ea271f562fd7ce95bb2a83b82_1440w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "49 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/493427555"}}, "attached_info": "ClQI5IST2KzZiqlmEAMaCDcxOTMxODI5IO7xvYsGMAA4KkApcgk0OTM0Mjc1NTV4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAPIBEwgBEg9kb21haW5fb3BlcmF0b3I="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "42_1634872061.953942", "card_id": "Q_493501489", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 95}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "两女子晚上住酒店密码锁被陌生人解开，店方称「不排除客人自导自演」，真实情况如何？入住酒店如何保障安全？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "10 月 19 日，来自上海的梁女士向极目新闻反映，17 日深夜，她在湖南长沙一酒店住店时，有人多次输入正确的密码，幸好房间门反锁才未被打开。梁女士事后得知，酒店房间门锁的密码是限时的，在入住时段外会失效，且只有住客和酒店工作人员知晓密码。该酒店负责人回应称，楼道内没有监控，无法确定开锁者是谁。此外，店方认为存在客人自导自演的可能。女子晚上住酒店密码锁被陌生人解开 店方：不排除客人自导自演"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-d4b9967f7841721569ce2d1f83f8b57c_720w.jpeg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "48 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/493501489"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I5IST2KzZiqlmEAMaCDcxOTQ4MjI0IPuFv4sGMBk42wJAKnIJNDkzNTAxNDg5eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "43_1634872061.9548001", "card_id": "Q_493004702", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 116}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "LGD 在 TI10 放猛犸，RNG 在 S7 放加里奥最后都输了，哪个更让你愤怒失望？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-7609b4b230a5eb9b9332339006f49314_720w.jpeg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "47 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/493004702"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I5IST2KzZiqlmEAMaCDcxODM4MDczILGGs4sGMAs4sAFAK3IJNDkzMDA0NzAyeACqAQli